name: The Metrics by mpeg - NEONZ Discord
description:
mpeg predicts "Sorry folks but this ain’t it; just looked at the metrics. This can’t sell out, I hope Tezos drops get there one day. Good luck."

NEONZ by Sutu is the first 10K pfp drop on tezos.  2,888 NEONZ sold in whitelist premint on 10/24/21. Public sale for remaining on 10/25/21 12pm PST.  This was minted ahead of public sale to commemorate what will go down as an all time bad take on Discord.
